Multiple award-winner DJ Spinall real name Sodamola Oluseye Desmond has released his album featuring many celebrated artists. The track Serious features Burna Boy and sounds nostalgic. Anyone familiar with Busta Rhymes will remember the track Dangerous released in 1997 which was an anthem of sorts in the late 90s and early 2000s. This, is, serious
We could make you delirious
You should have a healthy fear of us
‘Cause too much of us is dangerous… The track although has some parts seemingly paying tribute to Busta Rhymes’ Dangrous, It still has its own lines to make it a good party jam. Listen to the track below: 